result.name: Green Veggie

reviews.text: When it comes to Chinese vegetarian places, this is a great option. Located up in a building in the middle of the city, you can eat on a terrace, or sit inside. The food is very tasty and if you area missing meat, do order the char siew bun, very tasty vegetarian version of this famous grilled pork dish. The test of the food had great taste too and the service was quick and friendly.

The food quality is acceptable though a bit pricey. Service is ok but an experience make me disappointed. When I feedback about the unexpected spicy for the Green Veggie fried rice, the service lady told me I should inform them in advance if I cannot take too spicy food. However, there is no hint from the menu or their advanced advice about the recipe of it. So how come I able to tell it?  Felt frustrated ! And the dinning area is crowded.
Came here for lunch this time.  Good value for delicious vegetarian food.  The char siu bun was yum.
Good food and nice place

Green Veggie is the perfect place for vegetarians and they are vegan-friendly. They have a wide array of vegan food and great service too. The char siew bao, pork cutlet, lion mane mushroom and the rice with black fungus and mushroom dishes are absolutely delicious! I highly recommend this place!

result.name: 天然齋

reviews.text: 今天在回答問題時錯誤地點擊了永久結業。實際上至今尚在營業。謹此致歉。位處三樓。面積不大。但有專用的升降機。實在難得。其出品的齋菜中規中矩。大部份乘客慕名而來的。是其出品的叉燒包。包身鬆軟。叉燒味仿真。但口感與真的叉燒有距離。以傳統的叉燒包有分別。叉燒，包身，分碟上。每份六件。可點半份。最大的差異。客人可隨意的將齋叉燒，放入包中夾縫（三文治）然後進食。星期六下午二時30分開始。有較大嘅折扣優惠。
三餸飯堂食$50 跟湯連杯水，外賣自取$40，係中上環呢個真係良心價，因為大部份錢都用來交租金，另外員工比較友善。

When it comes to Chinese vegetarian places, this is a great option. Located up in a building in the middle of the city, you can eat on a terrace, or sit inside. The food is very tasty and if you area missing meat, do order the char siew bun, very tasty vegetarian version of this famous grilled pork dish. The test of the food had great taste too and the service was quick and friendly.
同事們時不時都會去食～Lunch Time有“雙送”揀～亦有“單點”揀，不過令街客好容易混肴坐邊，製造不必要的尷尬。。。

今晚最欣賞:芋頭魚，南瓜飯和义燒飽。
非常好吃。👍👍👍
